nl_querry: Please list the constructor names with 0 points at race 291. race at 291 refers to raceID = 291;
llm_querry: SELECT T1.name FROM constructors AS T1 JOIN constructorresults AS T2 ON T1.constructorId = T2.constructorId WHERE T2.raceId = 291 AND T2.points = 0
gold_querry: SELECT T2.name FROM constructorStandings AS T1 INNER JOIN constructors AS T2 ON T1.constructorId = T2.constructorId WHERE T1.points = 0 AND T1.raceId = 291
